            "table_note":"The person endings are **o / s / t / mus / tis / nt** — but a connecting vowel appears before each ending. For 'they', the connecting vowel is *-u-* not *-i-*, giving *-unt* not *-int*.\n\nA small group of 3rd conjugation verbs show *-io* in the 'I' form (e.g. *facio*, *facis*, *facit*, *facimus*, *facitis*, *faciunt*).\n\nColour key:\n**red** = connecting vowel\n**blue** = person ending",
            "infinitive_ending_header":"Ending",
        }],
